Bulgarian Tour
==============

ABDN project.
==============

About project:

* MainActivity use Tab Layou to render UI. Here are inflated two fragment. 
  One is grid view with all Cityes.
  Other use Recycle List to show short country history;

* When user click on Grig Item inflate another Paces Fragment and display all places for selected city. Data is populated with Recylcle List;

* Places fragment uses cardview to display data. On item click intend new Detail Activity;

* Detail Activity - show details about selected place. Image is stored inside CardView and text inside Scroll View;

* Single Tone Model - store data and shared between activities and fragments.

